=head1 NAME

	CL_RFC2671_4_1_quantity_OPT - The quantity of OPT pseudo-RRs


=head1 VERIFICATION POINTS

	Verify that a NUT transmits query that have correct number for OPT pseudo-RR

=begin html
	<UL>
	<DD><li>The quantity of OPT pseudo-RRs per message shall be either zero or one, 
	<DD>but not greater.
	</li>
	</ul> 

=end html

=head1 TARGET

	Client

=head1 SYNOPSIS

=begin html
<PRE>
	<A HREF="./CL_RFC2671_4_1_quantity_OPT.seq">CL_RFC2671_4_1_quantity_OPT.seq</A> [-tooloption ...]: KOI tool option
	See also <A HREF="../DNSConfig.pm">DNSConfig.pm</A>
</PRE>

=end html

